metadata.name: Fractured Memories - Metropolis
metadata.description:
Am I dreaming!  Am I awake!  I see the past or the future… Everything is vague… Everything is dark… Everything is fragile… Houses … Buildings … Human… Intertwined strands… 

Shapes made of strands as if they are exist or not. As if they appear for a moment and vanish in a blink of an eye. All the strands together form an image, image Of me, Of you, Of us… Of my city, Of your city, Of our city and of our world.

All of us with intertwined strands are connected in dreams. Why we are not seeing these strands in reality, Why are we so apart, Why we are not together.

So, Are we dreaming? Are we awake ?
Do we see the past or do we see the future?

Are these dreams happened in the past… or these dreams will happen in the future…
